# Performance — Do Not Regress

Performance work must **not** modify EPG sync files or Live TV UI patterns (see `apex-epg-live-tv-ui.mdc`).

## Invariants

| Area | Rule |
|------|------|
| **Indexer** | Chunk 50, 500ms pause; TMDB id-only in background (`details: nil`); no `ImageMemoryCache.purge` per chunk; tvOS skips `TextEmbedder` |
| **Indexer** | Pauses when: EPG sync gate, browse (`pauseForBrowse`), cloud sync, playback |
| **Launch** | `Task { await cloudSync.start() }` — never block launch `.task` on CloudKit |
| **Home** | Do not `@Observe` / bind `ContentIndexingService`; library heroes first; TMDB trending in background |
| **Tabs** | `lazyTab` mounts when `selection == tab`; call `pauseForBrowse()` on switch |
| **Cellular** | `NetworkMonitor.shouldProceedWithHeavyNetworkWork()` gates background indexer + EPG `syncIfDue` |
| **Images** | `CachedAsyncImage` keeps `.success` on re-eval; deferred purge on background only |
| **Collections** | Paginate Show All grids (100/page); cap favorites `@Query` limits |
| **TMDB detail** | Full enrichment on detail open (`resolveTMDBIdIfNeeded`); not in background indexer |

## Safe optimization targets

`ContentIndexer`, `HomeView+Trending`, `SearchView`, `LibraryCollectionRows`, `CloudSyncCoordinator` — not `LiveTVView` EPG state unless fixing a logged EPG UI bug.
